name: Spock Goal
tagline: Turn your effort into insightful NUMBER
body:
### Welcome to Spock Goal Pages This is an app to record how much time you have invested in building your skills. The basic idea of this app is based on the book Outliers - to be a real expert in any field, you should invest at least 10,000 hours of training. ### Download http://goo.gl/WdZXwg ![](http://i58.tinypic.com/10i8jsj.png) ![](http://i59.tinypic.com/2a7eclz.png) ### Authors and Contributors In 2014, Alan Sparrow (@alansparrow). ### Support or Contact Twitter: http://twitter.com/AlanSparrow9
Email: alansparrow19@gmail.com
Launchrock: http://spockgoal.launchrock.com/
